I thrifted this… interesting🤪, piece of art at the thrift store and knew it would be great for my bathroom’s empty wall. This piece of art has been up for a year now and I had to finally share. 

True story, I was nursing my son and my husband was like, “what are you doing with this creepy art that’s been in our mudroom for months”?! I told him I wanted to redesign it and he asked how and he said he would just do it since I knew wouldn’t 🤪

So, my husband took drywall spackle, smeared it with my direction and flung paint (my downstairs bathroom color) in it and signed the corner 😅

Ta da! ✨
Where’s the logic?! 🫠
